{"tid":199131,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲隻貓成日怪叫?","createTime":"2017-04-13T03:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T13:37:28.000Z","uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71c5fc6ab1e0212577088998d93e3dc4c40ee76b","tid":199131,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"隻貓唔係我養，但同佢fd過打band，由細<br />\n<br />\n到大都成日見。<br />\n<br />\n隻貓仲早過我出世，無廿幾，都有二十歲<br />\n<br />\n啦，好老。<br />\n<br />\n近幾年成日都怪叫，由其事係夜晚，唔係<br />\n<br />\nmeowmeow聲，都唔識形容，好似劏豬咁<br />\n<br />\n叫。無端白事係到叫，有無巴絲話我知究<br />\n<br />\n竟點解???叫春定點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋成日嘔，嘔水又有嘔罐頭魚又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc7330392145ed92d146323a53e21345819c1dd","tid":199131,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"叫春啊嘛"},{"pid":"119fb951be5388efca28a1b3f6fcd39c2baeaf69","tid":199131,"uid":33961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"帶佢睇獸醫啦<br />\n<br />\n我隻貓都係叫同嘔, 睇獸醫發現腎有事, 醫左一星期都救唔返要打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5551fe2eb24825d773320bae9084ddd31b2ca82a","tid":199131,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"白事"},{"pid":"af8596611ad556e1826487fb2cec24b7dc96b2de","tid":199131,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶佢睇獸醫啦<br />\n<br />\n我隻貓都係叫同嘔, 睇獸醫發現腎有事, 醫左一星期都救唔返要打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾歲命呀?"},{"pid":"9685c48a5f368794c9c857f5068269ee29cd323a","tid":199131,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:36:24.000Z","msg":"應該唔舒服，睇下獸醫好d"},{"pid":"7ff1f528295539c090a0ed5f1c7164bc582c7120","tid":199131,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"平時又好精神，行得走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9321dc38d172fc8dba0c0e6a05da3dca5712e6ec","tid":199131,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時又好精神，行得走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n年紀大好難講<br />\n加上佢唔會識得話比你聽邊度唔舒服<br />\n咁老嘅貓做下身體檢查無壞<br />\n睇下腎指數果d正唔正常"},{"pid":"604aa6ddbbfd356f54ae70488cd24b997e04c528","tid":199131,"uid":74309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"有一次屋企買左新櫃有鏡<br />\n我屋企隻貓係深夜望住塊鏡發出<br />\nO niao niao niao niao<br />\n咁樣既叫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇到我呢 仲以為唔知咩黎"},{"pid":"bde9deef68c922e061debb1ebdab166b94832f78","tid":199131,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:29:56.000Z","msg":"20歲都未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb4fcb5f8825d2c088577fd11f9d2ff5d8c3202","tid":199131,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我隻貓成日一見唔到我就嗌到好似bb仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}